title: BONUS: Latto Full Interview + Kandi Burruss of Real Housewives Of Atlanta
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Latto stepped up to Ebro in the Morning and had a fun, candid conversation in which they discussed a variety of topics including her passion for rap music, the origin behind her name change, Ebro's reaction to 'Big Energy', what makes her different, the social media outrage over her feature tease, and much more! Her album '777' is set to be released soon! 

Kandi Burruss sits down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss her brand new show 'Kandi & The Gang' which airs Sundays at 9PM EST on Bravo! She also discusses her return to Real Housewives Of Atlanta, if Xscape will return, working with her family, acting on The Chi, sex toy line, and more! 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
